original_title: ROH & NJPW: War of The Worlds - Night 1
overview: War of the Worlds '15 featured eight professional wrestling matches that involved different wrestlers from pre-existing scripted feuds and storylines. Wrestlers portrayed villains, heroes, or less distinguishable characters in the scripted events that built tension and culminated in a wrestling match or series of matches.
title: ROH & NJPW: War of The Worlds - Night 1
